Title: Ratio<br>
<br>
Stamenent:<br>
<br>
Given a sentence,output the ratio of the total number of <b>alphabets</b> in the sentence to the total number of <b>words</b> in the sentence.
<br><br>
Input:<br>
<br>
First line contains an integer 't' indicating the number of test cases<br><br>
<br><br>
next 't' lines contain a single sentence 's' containing alphabets and punctuations.
<br><br>
Output:<br>
<br>
For each case output an integer representing the ratio in a single line.<br>
Truncate the decimal parts of the division between total number of alphabets and total number of words.
<br><br>
Constraints:<br>
<br>
t < 50<br>
<br>
length of is s < = 200<br>
<br>
Sample Input: <br>
<br>
1<br>
I love CODEMSRIT.<br>
<br>
Sample Output:<br>
4<br>
